{
  "stem": "188.1",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they recruited some former teachers or retired teachers, whatever.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And it was a very long distance for me to go.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We were also told we were no longer allowed to ride our bikes.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So I had to either walk, or I could use a scooter.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And from one day to the next, I became number one hypochondriac.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I had, every morning, a stomachache.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I couldn't go to school.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Days that I went to school, I got physically ill at school.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I think I was-- I was not so much frightened as I felt truly displaced and-- and pulled out of my environment, away from my friends.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was among total strangers.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was forced to do something.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And that lasted almost a year.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Close to a year.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "In the meantime, we had more problems at home.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We had mobs that had thrown rocks into windows.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] They congregated at night and were trying to demolish my parents' business.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I remember I had-- I slept upstairs, in the front of the-- of the house.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I remember a rock coming into the bedroom and more or less shearing right by my head.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So these are vivid memories still, which I haven't actually thought about much until now.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I've suppressed them.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] Pretty soon after that, [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] we were-- we had limitations, as far as the hours that we were allowed out.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So I saw less of my relatives, and-- [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] and some never again.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I'm thinking of some of my cousins, my aunts and uncles, my grandfather, that I never-- never saw again.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My father's parents went into hiding, and they survived the war.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And my maternal grandmother survived the war.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
